wiki.content:
Officially released on August 7, 2009. (digitally first)
  
 "TiK ToK" is a dance track by pop singer Ke$ha. The song has climbed the Billboard charts and was the very first #1 song on the Billboard Hot 100 of the year 2010.
 
 Songwriters: Lukasz Gottwald, Benjamin Levin, Kesha Rose Sebert
 Publishers: DYNAMITE COP MUSIC, KASZ MONEY PUBLISHING, MATZA BALL MUSIC,
          WHERE DA KASZ AT?
